title: Gov. Fallin Names Payne County Sheriff R.B. Hauf to OSBI Commission (The Office of the ...
text: ( Source : The Office of the Governor of the State of Oklahoma ) OKLAHOMA CITY - Governor Mary Fallin today announced she has appointed Payne County Sheriff R.B. Hauf to serve on the Oklahoma State Bureau of Investigation ( OSBI ) Commission .
